✅ Self-Healing Workflow
	•	If an EC2 instance becomes unhealthy:
	•	ALB health check marks it as failed.
	•	ASG terminates the failed instance.
	•	ASG launches a new instance automatically.
	•	ALB rechecks and rebalances traffic.


